---
title: Chicken and Basil Stir-Fry with Snap Peas and Carrots
description: We're bringing a taste of Thailand into your home tonight
with a delicious chicken stir-fry. Thai basil is the heartier
cousin to the delicate Italian basil, and stands up to strong
flavours like fish sauce and chili-garlic sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-basil-stir-fry-c673167d.jpg
